On the GEVids YouTube channel, we create highly edited Minecraft challenges and skits. All videos on this channel are my original creations, and have NOT been taken from another channel. For our short form content, we program each character individually to make a scene come to life, featuring action packed scenarios, friendship, betrayal, and more.
